Crew of the Admiral Kuznetsov fitted old MiG-15 engine to the front of a tractor .
They fitted the contraption with a diffuser, spreading the air out over the deck .
The vehicle was then driven up and down the 1,000ft deck, blowing all debris overboard .
It is the jewel in President Putin's military fleet, carrying 18 fighter jets and 17 anti-submarine helicopters .